#This recipe is for Chicken Karhai, a delicious tomato curry based dish

Ingredients
Bone-in chicken 	2 pounds
Salt			2 teaspoons
Red chili powder	2 teaspoons
Cumin powder		3 teaspoons
Turmeric powder		1/2 teaspoon
Tomatoes (Roma, small)	6	
Fenugreek leaaves 	1 teaspoon
Garam Masala		1/2 teaspoon
Oil			1/2 cup
Ginger Garlic Past	4 teaspoon

